OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1779970272
OL,3,CPolice recover body after teenager
OL,4,Creported missing at Hampshire lake
OL,6,FA body has been found in a search for
OL,7,Fa teenager who went missing whilst
OL,8,Fswimming at a lake near Blackwater, in
OL,9,FHampshire.
OL,11,FHampshire and Isle of Wight Police
OL,12,Fsaid officers recovered a body from
OL,13,FHawley Lake this afternoon.
OL,15,FA formal identification process has
OL,16,Fnot yet taken place, but the family of
OL,17,Fthe missing boy have been notified,
OL,18,Fthe force said.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
