OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1779970272
OL,3,CPolice recover body after teenager
OL,4,Creported missing at Hampshire lake
OL,6,FIt follows a multi-agency search,
OL,7,Fwhich involved marine and drone units,
OL,8,Fthe National Police Air Service
OL,9,F(NPAS), fire service, Hampshire Search
OL,10,Fand Rescue, and divers from the
OL,11,FMetropolitan Police.
OL,13,FThe force said the boy was first
OL,14,Freported missing at 3:28pm on Tuesday.
OL,16,FA police cordon has been set up around
OL,17,Fthe area.
OL,19,FHawley Lake Sail Training Centre said
OL,20,Fit has closed its entire site today
OL,21,Fdue to the police presence.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
