OL,3,CPolice recover body after teenager
OL,4,Creported missing at Hampshire lake
OL,6,FIt's asking members not to visit the
OL,7,Fclub "unless absolutely necessary".
OL,9,F"We will update you when we have an
OL,10,Findication of when our activities will
OL,11,Fbe allowed to resume, in the meantime
OL,12,Fplease refrain from asking questions
OL,13,Fas we are currently unable to provide
OL,14,Ffurther information," the club said in
OL,15,Fa statement.
